             was indicted for <rs id="t18161030-25-off128" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18161030-25-off128" type="offenceCategory" value="violentTheft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18161030-25-off128" type="offenceSubcategory" value="highwayRobbery"></interp>
               feloniously assaulting 
                     
                        <persName id="t18161030-25-victim271" type="victimName">
                           James John 
                           Sheath
                        <interp inst="t18161030-25-victim271" type="surname" value="Sheath"></interp>
