                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18161030-25-defend269 t18161030-25-punish132"></join>
               DEATH
            </rs>, aged 23.</p>
               <p>First Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Justice Dallas.</p>
